{"format": "tiptap/v1", "updatedAt": "2026-06-22T04:21:18.644Z", "doc": {"type": "doc", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Artificial Intelligence (AI)"}, {"type": "text", "text": " is the broadest field: it’s the capability of a computer system to perform tasks that normally require human intelligence—such as learning, reasoning, perception, and decision-making."}]}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"src": "data:image/svg+xml;base64,", "alt": "What is AI — concept overview"}}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "How AI fits into the hierarchy AI → ML → DL → Gen AI"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "The relationship is nested (each term is a subset of the previous):"}]}, {"type": "codeBlock", "attrs": {"language": "text"}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "AI (Artificial Intelligence)\n └── ML (Machine Learning)\n      └── DL (Deep Learning)\n           └── Gen AI (Generative AI, often using DL models like LLMs)"}]}, {"type": "bulletList", "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "AI"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Mimics human intelligence; includes rule-based systems, search, planning, and ML approaches"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "ML"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": A subset of AI where algorithms learn patterns from data without being explicitly programmed for each task"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "DL"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": A specialized subset of ML using multi-layer artificial neural networks to handle complex patterns (e.g., image/speech recognition)"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Gen AI"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": A specialized capability (often built on DL) that "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "italic"}], "text": "creates new content"}, {"type": "text", "text": "—text, images, code, music—rather than just classifying or predicting"}]}]}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Classical Machine Learning vs. Generative AI"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Within AI, there are two major approaches:"}]}, {"type": "table", "content": [{"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Aspect"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Classical (Traditional) Machine Learning"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Generative AI"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Goal"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Pattern recognition, classification, regression, prediction"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Create "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "italic"}], "text": "new"}, {"type": "text", "text": " content similar to training data"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Model type"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Often discriminative (learns boundaries between classes)"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Generative (learns data distribution to sample new examples)"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Examples"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Netflix recommendations, fraud detection, logistic regression, decision trees"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "ChatGPT, DALL·E, AI art tools, code generators"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Output"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Label, score, or prediction (e.g., “fraud/not fraud”)"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Novel text, image, audio, video, or code"}]}]}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Classical ML"}, {"type": "text", "text": " is “discriminative”: it learns to distinguish between categories (e.g., cat vs. dog).\n"}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Generative AI"}, {"type": "text", "text": " is “generative”: it learns the underlying probability distribution of data and can generate new samples from it (e.g., draw a new cat image)."}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Mental model"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Think of AI as “intelligent behavior,” ML as “learning from data,” DL as “learning with deep neural networks,” and Gen AI as “using those networks to "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "italic"}], "text": "create"}, {"type": "text", "text": " new things.” Classical ML is the older, prediction-focused branch; Gen AI is the newer, creation-focused branch built primarily on deep learning."}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Key takeaways"}, {"type": "text", "text": "\n- AI is the overarching field; ML, DL, and Gen AI are all subsets of AI.\n- Classical ML = discriminative, prediction/classification; Gen AI = generative, content creation.\n- Gen AI typically relies on deep learning (e.g., transformers, GANs, diffusion models)."}]}]}}